<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Employee Identity Template</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      html, body {
        height: 100%;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f3f4f6;
      }

      .wrapper {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 100vh;
        padding: 0.5rem;
      }

      .page {
        position: relative;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 794px;
        height: 1123px;
        padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
        background-color: white;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-between;
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      .blank {
        display: inline-block;
        border-bottom: 1px dotted #999;
        min-width: 150px;
        height: 20px;
      }

      .long-blank {
        min-width: 300px;
      }

      @media print {
        .wrapper {
          padding: 0;
          min-height: 0;
        }
        .page {
          width: 210mm;
          height: 297mm;
          box-shadow: none;
          margin: 0;
          padding: 10mm;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="page">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div>
          <div class="relative border-b-8 border-blue-700 pb-6 mb-10">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between flex-col sm:flex-row">
              <div class="text-center sm:text-left">
                <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-800 tracking-wide">
                  DOTLABS.AI
                </h1>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic">
                  Smart. Simple. Scalable.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center sm:text-right mt-2 sm:mt-0">
                <p class="text-sm">
                  Date: <span class="blank long-blank"></span>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute left-0 bottom-0 w-40 h-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-800 to-cyan-400 transform -rotate-2"></div>
          </div>

          <!-- Main Content -->
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-700 border-b pb-1 border-blue-500">
              Employee Information
            </h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-16 gap-y-4">
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-600">Full Name</p>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-900"><span class="blank long-blank"></span></p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-600">Email Address</p>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-900"><span class="blank long-blank"></span></p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-600">Department</p>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-900"><span class="blank long-blank"></span></p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-600">Employee ID</p>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-900"><span class="blank"></span></p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Description -->
            <div class="mt-8 p-6 border-l-4 border-blue-600 bg-blue-50 shadow-sm text-justify space-y-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
              <p>
                <span class="blank"></span> has officially been recognized as a trusted and
                essential part of Dotlabs.ai. As an active contributor in the
                <span class="blank"></span> department, their role significantly impacts
                our mission to build intelligent, user-friendly systems.
              </p>

              <p>
                Joining Dotlabs.ai means more than just being part of a company —
                it means becoming part of a vision. <span class="blank"></span> continues to
                showcase integrity, commitment, and innovation. Their email address,
                <span class="blank long-blank"></span>, serves as a contact point for support.
              </p>

              <p>
                This document formally acknowledges the credibility and
                responsibility entrusted to <span class="blank long-blank"></span>. It is also a
                symbol of gratitude for the consistent performance and passion
                demonstrated day after day.
              </p>

              <p>
                As we move into the future of AI and smart systems, Dotlabs.ai
                believes our collective strength lies in people like
                <span class="blank"></span>. Through teamwork and visionary
                thinking, we lead industries — together.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer & QR -->
        <div class="relative mt-auto pt-10">
          <div class="absolute right-0 bottom-24 text-center">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-1">Scan to verify identity</p>
            <img
              src="<%= qrCode %>"
              alt="QR Code"
              class="w-28 h-28 border-2 border-gray-300 shadow-lg inline-block"
            />
          </div>

          <footer class="w-full border-t-8 border-blue-700 pt-4 pb-3 text-center text-sm text-gray-600 bg-white">
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center items-center space-y-2 sm:space-y-0 sm:space-x-10 text-blue-800 font-medium mb-2">
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-1">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4a8 8 0 100 16 8 8 0 000-16zm0 0v16m8-8H4" />
                </svg>
                <a href="https://www.dotlabs.ai" class="hover:underline">www.dotlabs.ai</a>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-center space-x-1">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16 12H8m0 0l4-4m-4 4l4 4" />
                </svg>
                <a href="mailto:career@dotlabs.ai" class="hover:underline">career@dotlabs.ai</a>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-center space-x-1">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 5h2l3.6 7.59-1.35 2.44A1 1 0 008 17h8a1 1 0 001-1v-1H9.42a.25.25 0 01-.23-.15L8.1 13h7.45a1 1 0 00.92-.61l3.24-7.24a1 1 0 00-.92-1.39H5.21" />
                </svg>
                <span>+123 456 7890</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">
              © <span class="blank"></span> Dotlabs.ai. All rights reserved.
            </p>
          </footer>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
